A cyberpunk-style digital visualization of thousands of glowing interconnected nodes forming a massive network web, each node representing a person with neon blue and magenta connection lines streaming between them. The scene is set in a dark, rain-slicked virtual environment with holographic data streams cascading in the background. In the foreground, a single bright central node pulses with energy as countless smaller nodes branch outward in an organic tree-like pattern, their connections creating an intricate luminous spider web against the black void. Chrome and glass surfaces reflect the network's glow, with subtle grid lines suggesting a digital matrix beneath everything.
